---
/**
 * AboutSection Component
 *
 * "Where life begins" intro section for the home page.
 *
 * Usage:
 *   <AboutSection />
 */
---

<section class="about-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="sr-only">River of Life - Apostolic Pentecostal Church in Henry, IL</h1>
    <h2>Where life begins</h2>
    <p>Whether you're exploring faith for the first time or looking for a church to call home, you'll find a welcoming community here. We're real people on a real journeyâ€”and there's a place for you.</p>
    <a href="/about" class="text-link">Learn more about us &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-section .container {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-script);
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-section p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .text-link {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-teal);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .text-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-teal-dark);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-section {
      padding: 2rem 1.25rem;
    }
    .about-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .about-section p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
